{"tid":691143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：蠱惑的閘攔路　霸氣消防照拆","createTime":"2018-06-05T12:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T15:17:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61d4dbd840bb88db8d8af84a1a2c9217f2456f39","tid":691143,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180605/20411412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F20411412&d=NsE7wDIgqlO59o5HwdL985WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a6e80e5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F20411412&h=56047092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180605/20411412</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月05日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：蠱惑的閘攔路　霸氣消防照拆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180605/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180605%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=4236e6e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n救人一命，勝造七級浮屠。近日facebook流傳一段消防車疑似被停車場閘門擋路嘅片，有霸氣消防員突然雙手出擊，將閘門拆去，以便消防車進入。拍片人唔止無埋怨，仲讚賞消防員「呢啲先係做嘢㗎」。<br />\n<br />\n樓主以「火速救兵 VS安定閘口」為題，現場據知係屯門安定邨，停車場閘門出名係「蠱惑的閘」，成日拍八達通都無反應，又試過「俾人衝甩過兩次」，但係「轉頭就裝返上去」。樓主話當日消防去到閘前，搞咗一輪都開唔到閘，先至逼「霸氣消防員」出手拆走道閘，最終消除「路障」後，4架消防車暢通無阻咁進入屋苑救援。<br />\n<br />\n樓主話喎，拍片人連聲大嗌消防好嘢、做到嘢。其實道閘成日都short short哋，唔畀車過，消防咁做，都算係「為民除害」啩？  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：港鐵「唔暢順」落車要手動　神力乘客擘開幕門<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：結他發燒友樂器舖偷粒「的」"},{"pid":"d0fa6d2d5ea1e1060e2d5cd8a5d38653e2619701","tid":691143,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"對消防嚟講，碎料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a77283afcbdf13581728a78c6b67f14c397518","tid":691143,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"直接撞撚爛去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e94d10b75ff7523d9737bcddf4e0e8569d748c","tid":691143,"uid":143572,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"番到局再睇下個閘有冇違反消防例。搞多佢一次。"},{"pid":"ef8071bb46b08fde60cc7f6404ed5d5257f60aef","tid":691143,"uid":42435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"鄉音食Q阿姐：阿蛇梨味伯吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752f9375929ebe781bddf3ac4d0e010a6318bb30","tid":691143,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8a77283afcbdf13581728a78c6b67f14c397518","tid":691143,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"直接撞撚爛去啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"東方聽日頭版"},{"pid":"5e76b14dcc4b15fd3f889a5e7fa6bbda23c94c9b","tid":691143,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"呢道閘設計上預左俾緊急車撞 係香港呢個荒謬次地下下要報警條條賠$5000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399eb627f3c84a4ee58eba1c80dfbabe097fb902","tid":691143,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}